# Phase 2 context budget

Follow [AGENTS.md](../AGENTS.md) Â§ Context loading. Do not preload planning docs.

## Doc boundaries

| Load | When |
|------|------|
| `AGENTS.md`, `docs/phase2-implementation-spec.md` | Always (once per session) |
| `services/state-service/AGENTS.md` | Go State Service work |
| `services/alert-service/AGENTS.md` | Go Alert Service work |
